{"tid":1152341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲大選在即 總理承諾5%首期上車","createTime":"2019-05-13T01:34:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T02:35:07.000Z","uid":28765,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5b4a115be029f6397c3ad95b1f6f6f4a7436e387","tid":1152341,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T01:34:40.000Z","msg":"澳洲大選將於下周六（18日）舉行，總理莫里森（Scott Morrison）為競逐連任，推出重大民生競選承諾-「首置客首期降至5%」吸選票。<br />\n<br />\n計劃重點內容是，將首次置業者首期由20%大幅減至5%，二人家庭年收入不多於20萬澳元，或個人年收入低於12.5萬澳元者均符合資格參與計劃，餘下的按揭貸款則由國家房屋融資公司（National Housing Finance and Investment Corporation）提供擔保。<br />\n<br />\n莫里森指，現時澳洲市民平均需時9至10年籌備首期，料計劃可助市民減低首期支出，盡快完成置業夢想。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190512/59593278\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190512%2F59593278&d=JinSrGH%2FoctmVpTuEhnihNagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=90a66ab8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190512%2F59593278&h=e064eb4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190512/59593278</a>"},{"pid":"81036c27b47557deb26e16ce3f0498b956046730","tid":1152341,"uid":56698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T01:36:04.000Z","msg":"推高樓價"},{"pid":"ce511f34dcf5c89fdaf6afb50be392cd2069f59c","tid":1152341,"uid":191762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T01:36:12.000Z","msg":"工黨1.13倍<br />\nLiberal 5倍"},{"pid":"62c3c49e6b0139442dd1c1d0794b9c734733b44e","tid":1152341,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T01:38:00.000Z","msg":"你睇下，香港政府反而加你首期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4267773f0f2a6872a782667001a9879c1ff4b731","tid":1152341,"uid":221650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T01:42:06.000Z","msg":"G 持<